sub_title: Designer Menswear // Consultant Sustainability in the Fashion Supply chain
summary:
https://www.instagram.com/femke.van.e/ 

Highly creative and multi-talented Fashion Designer with extensive experience in menswear industry. Artistic and analytical skills to create new fashion sketches, technical drawings, and colour palettes. Excellent leadership and business acumen talent with success delivering high-level marketing and revenue-generating design programmes. Exceptional interpersonal skills; able to build strong rapport with clients and staff, drive product life-cycle, and co-ordinate design changes. Enthusiastic innovator, competency in technology adaptation and component development while focusing on quality standards.

PRODUCTION MANAGEMENT
- Product Development Life-cycle
- Menswear Designs Forming
- Mood Boards & Fabrics Formulation
- Photography & Trends Analysis

DESIGN PROJECT MANAGEMENT
- Technical Drawings Creation
-  Performance Evaluation
- Client Acquisition
- Team Training & Leadership

BUSINESS GROWTH
- Collection Launches
- Opportunities Identification
- Campaign Planning
- Brand Advertising & Promotions
